<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَقُلْتُ اجْعَلِي ضَوْءَ الْفَرَاقِدِ كُلِّهَا ... يَمِينًا وَمِهْرَ النِّسْرِ عَنْ شِمَالِكِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَقَالَ آخَرٌ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَسِيرُوا بِقَلْبِ الْعَقْرَبِ الْيَوْمَ إِنَّهُ ... سَوَاءٌ عَلَيْكُمْ بِالنُّحُوسِ وَبِالسَّعْدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَيْ:</span> سِيرُوا عِنْدَ سُقُوطِ قَلْبِ الْعَقْرَبِ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَالْعَرَبُ يَقُولُونَ:</span> إِنَّهُ نَحْسٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَقَالَ آخَرٌ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>قَدْ جَاءَ سَعْدٌ مَوْعِدًا بِشَرِّهِ ... مُخَبِّرَةً جُنُودُهُ بِحَرِّهِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>